channel.title: The International Forum
channel.description:
[center][b][u]The International Forums[/u][/b][/center] Yes thats right! The International Forums, We are trying our best to get Community! We hope you come out! We would love for you to see what we done, And what you can do there!
[url=http://thenationalforum.ulmb.com/index.php]The International Forums! CLICK HERE![/url]
What we have on these forums is many things, and we are still working on alot more! Well for starters Im the Owner of the Forums. But dont worry. I wont bother you one bit. But here you can...
[ul][li]Welcome Board - Introduce yourself. We would love to see you :)[/li] [li]Business - You can meet people from all around the world for Business![/li] [li]Articles - Make Articles and even get payed for them! You can make from $1- $500.[/li] [li]World News - All about whats going on with the world! Dont you want to know?[/li] [li]Advertisement - Come Advertise whatever you want! Websites to Products![/li] [li]Myspace - Discuss about Myspace here! Getting to know a new person is fun[/li] [li]HomeWork Help - Still in grade school and need help? People here will help you![/li] [li]Private Servers - Runescape Private Servers, its a game Online! Really Fun here![/li][/ul]
We have many many things on these forums that you would love to do here! what? had a hard day? Well then grab a Cup of Coffee or some Hot Chocolate and sit back on our Cafe! Speak to many people here.
You can get on our Development team and be Moderation, Administration.
MERRY CHRISTMAS! Come here And speak the word! To all about How Merry Christmas is! In real Time Christmas stands for= Christ-Mass, Mass means your Celebrating the Day he died. And giving respect to him.
Say what? Saw something Incredible!? Say it here! We would love to find out whats going on!
Our Community is helpful, and they listen very well.. Have any problems with your life and want to figure it out, well ask it. and we would answer... Once you've joined.. Your family to us! Remember that!
[url=http://thenationalforum.ulmb.com/index.php]The International Forums! CLICK HERE![/url]
